                  <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Constructive dismissal can arise from a single serious breach, or from a "last straw" where a series of smaller incidents cumulatively destroyed trust and confidence. A clear pattern of behaviour over time can be just as powerful as one major incident.
                  </p>
